"font-family:pridi,serif;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0em;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">El Fenicio es un velero IMX40 dise&ntilde;ado por los arquitectos navales Niels y Lars Jeppesen, del que se han construido solo 100 unidades en los astilleros daneses X-YACHT. Este modelo ha participado en importantes regatas del circuito internacional a lo largo de los &uacute;ltimos 20 a&ntilde;os, como la Sydney Hobart o la Fasnet, cosechando en todas ellas grandes resultados, cosa que ahora los fenicios nos disponemos a emular... &nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:24px; line-height:normal;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:24px; line-height:normal;\"><span class=\"color_43 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-style:italic;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-family:pridi,serif;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0em;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Datos t&eacute;cnicos del IMX 40:</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul class=\"color_43 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:pridi, serif; font-size:24px; font-style:italic; font-weight:normal; text-align:left;\">\n<li style=\"line-height:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:24px; line-height:normal;\"><span class=\"color_43 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-style:italic;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-family:pridi,serif;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0em;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Tipo: Velero de regata</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li style=\"line-height:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:24px; line-height:normal;\"><span class=\"color_43 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-style:italic;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-family:pridi,serif;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0em;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Localizaci&oacute;n: Marina de las Salinas, San Pedro del Pinatar (Murcia)</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li style=\"line-height:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:24px; line-height:normal;\"><span class=\"color_43 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-style:italic;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-family:pridi,serif;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0em;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Nombre: Fenicio</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li style=\"line-height:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:24px; line-height:normal;\"><span class=\"color_43 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-style:italic;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-family:pridi,serif;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0em;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Astillero: X-Yachts</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li style=\"line-height:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:24px; line-height:normal;\"><span class=\"color_43 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-style:italic;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-family:pridi,serif;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0em;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Bandera: Espa&ntilde;ola</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li style=\"line-height:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:24px; line-height:normal;\"><span class=\"color_43 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-style:italic;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-family:pridi,serif;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0em;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Material: PRFV reforzado con fibra de carbono</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4 class=\"font_4 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:24px; line-height:normal;\"><span class=\"color_43 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-style:italic;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-family:pridi,serif;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0em;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Dimensiones:</span></span></span></span></span></span></h4>\n\n<ul class=\"color_43 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:pridi, serif; font-size:24px; font-style:italic; font-weight:normal; text-align:left;\">\n<li style=\"line-height:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:24px; line-height:normal;\"><span class=\"color_43 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-style:italic;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-family:pridi,serif;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Eslora: 12.10 m</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li style=\"line-height:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:24px; line-height:normal;\"><span class=\"color_43 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-style:italic;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-family:pridi,serif;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0em;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Manga: 4.20 m</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li style=\"line-height:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:24px; line-height:normal;\"><span class=\"color_43 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-style:italic;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-family:pridi,serif;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0em;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Calado: 2.45 m</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li style=\"line-height:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:24px; line-height:normal;\"><span class=\"color_43 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-style:italic;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-family:pridi,serif;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0em;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Desplazamiento: 6475 Kg</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4 class=\"font_4 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:24px; line-height:normal;\"><span class=\"color_43 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-style:italic;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-family:pridi,serif;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0em;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Capacidad</span></span></span></span></span></span></h4>\n\n<ul class=\"color_43 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:pridi, serif; font-size:24px; font-style:italic; font-weight:normal; text-align:left;\">\n<li style=\"line-height:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:24px; line-height:normal;\"><span class=\"color_43 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-style:italic;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-family:pridi,serif;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0em;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">M&aacute;ximo de tripulantes: 10</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li style=\"line-height:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:24px; line-height:normal;\"><span class=\"color_43 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-style:italic;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-family:pridi,serif;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0em;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Cabinas: 3</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li style=\"line-height:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:24px; line-height:normal;\"><span class=\"color_43 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-style:italic;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-family:pridi,serif;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0em;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Literas: 3</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li style=\"line-height:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:24px; line-height:normal;\"><span class=\"color_43 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-style:italic;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-family:pridi,serif;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0em;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Aseos: 1</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li style=\"line-height:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:24px; line-height:normal;\"><span class=\"color_43 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-style:italic;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-family:pridi,serif;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0em;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Capacidad de agua: 400 L</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4 class=\"font_4 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:24px; line-height:normal;\"><span class=\"color_43 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-style:italic;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-family:pridi,serif;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0em;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Motorizaci&oacute;n</span></span></span></span></span></span></h4>\n\n<ul class=\"color_43 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-family:pridi, serif; font-size:24px; font-style:italic; font-weight:normal; text-align:left;\">\n<li style=\"line-height:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:24px; line-height:normal;\"><span class=\"color_43 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-style:italic;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-family:pridi,serif;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0em;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">N&uacute;mero de motores: 1</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li style=\"line-height:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">\n<p class=\"font_8 wixui-rich-text__text\" style=\"font-size:24px; line-height:normal;\"><span class=\"color_43 wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-style:italic;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"font-family:pridi,serif;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0em;\" class=\"wixui-rich-text__text\">Potencia: 40 CV</span></span></span></s